WEBVTT

00:00.355 --> 00:01.581
<i>Previously on "Switched at Birth"...</i>

00:01.909 --> 00:03.463
You took home someone else's baby

00:03.463 --> 00:05.400
and another family took home yours.

00:05.400 --> 00:08.048
Does anybody know where
this other child might be?

00:08.870 --> 00:11.195
I'm so glad you found it.

00:11.338 --> 00:12.175
Nice to meet you.

00:12.241 --> 00:13.143
Who's my father?

00:13.466 --> 00:15.496
It's a guy who took off
when Daphne was little

00:15.496 --> 00:16.804
and hasn't been in touch since.

00:16.941 --> 00:19.825
Did he leave because I'm deaf?

00:20.257 --> 00:21.477
Angelo Sorrento's my dad.

00:21.477 --> 00:23.059
I'm Angelo Sorrento's daughter.

00:23.633 --> 00:25.341
We found this guitar pick in his car.

00:25.669 --> 00:26.752
There are pictures of Bay

00:26.769 --> 00:28.000
when she was four years old.

00:28.082 --> 00:29.308
How do you have these?

00:29.499 --> 00:31.464
I found out 12 and a half years ago.

00:34.437 --> 00:36.605
Do you ever speak...

00:37.308 --> 00:39.575
like with your voice?

00:39.727 --> 00:43.345
There is one person who's
always been there for me.

00:43.380 --> 00:45.481
Emmett.

